  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Manicurist",
  "description": "<h2>Job Summary</h2><p>We are seeking a <strong>skilled and customer-oriented Manicurist / Nail Technician</strong> to join our salon. The ideal candidate is passionate about nail care, maintains high hygiene standards, and delivers excellent service to ensure a positive and professional experience for all clients.</p><h2>Key Roles & Responsibilities</h2><ul><li><p>Perform professional <strong>manicure and pedicure services</strong>, including basic, gel, and spa treatments</p></li><li><p>Provide <strong>nail enhancements</strong> such as gel polish, acrylics, extensions, and nail art (where applicable)</p></li><li><p>Consult clients on nail care, styles, colours, and suitable treatments</p></li><li><p>Maintain <strong>strict hygiene and sanitation standards</strong> in accordance with salon policies</p></li><li><p>Clean, disinfect, and properly store tools, equipment, and workstations</p></li><li><p>Deliver friendly, attentive, and professional customer service</p></li><li><p>Manage appointments efficiently and respect clients’ time</p></li><li><p>Recommend and promote salon services or retail products when appropriate</p></li><li><p>Identify nail or skin conditions and advise clients accordingly</p></li><li><p>Follow salon SOPs, safety procedures, and workplace policies</p></li></ul><h2>Job Requirements & Qualifications</h2><h3>Mandatory Requirements:</h3><ul><li><p>Proven experience as a <strong>Manicurist / Nail Technician</strong></p></li><li><p>Knowledge of <strong>nail care techniques, tools, and products</strong></p></li><li><p>Understanding of <strong>hygiene, sanitation, and safety standards</strong></p></li><li><p>Good communication and interpersonal skills</p></li><li><p>Customer-focused with a professional attitude</p></li><li><p>Willingness to work flexible hours, including weekends and public holidays</p></li></ul><h3>Preferred / Advantage:</h3><ul><li><p>Relevant <strong>beauty or nail certification</strong></p></li><li><p>Experience with <strong>gel nails, extensions, nail art, or spa treatments</strong></p></li><li><p>Experience working in a professional salon environment</p></li></ul><h2>Physical & Work Requirements</h2><ul><li><p>Ability to sit or stand for extended periods</p></li><li><p>Good hand-eye coordination and attention to detail</p></li><li><p>Comfortable working with nail products and chemicals using safe practices</p></li></ul><h2>What We Offer</h2><ul><li><p>Competitive salary with commissions and tips (where applicable)</p></li><li><p>Training and skill development opportunities</p></li><li><p>Supportive and professional work environment</p></li><li><p>Career growth opportunities</p></li></ul>",
